# Instagram Content Generator - Environment Variables

# 1. Google Gemini API Key (Required for AI content generation)
# Get one at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# 2. GNews API Key (Required for fetching live news)
# Get one at: https://gnews.io/
GNEWS_API_KEY=your_gnews_api_key_here

# 3. Instagram Automation Session (Managed by saveSession script)
# No manual key needed, but storage.json must exist.
